        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d31229.299169406848!2d28.71218221591002!3d60.71178771916179!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x46973232203b6cbb%3A0xc0c46abf336b4e55!2z0JLRi9Cx0L7RgNCzLCDQm9C10L3QuNC90LPRgNCw0LTRgdC60LDRjyDQvtCx0Lsu!5e0!3m2!1sru!2sru!4v1711013569269!5m2!1sru!2sru" width="1200" height="350" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
